“Shockingly, a blast of shots was heard hours later. The officer in charge of the base rushed to the scene only to find the lifeless body of the victim in the driver's seat of his Toyota Probox.”
The DCI said Mr Mokamba had been socially chewing miraa with the deceased.
“He was disarmed and arrested, having sprayed 10 rounds of ammunition in the blast.”



