Mr Mokamba was placed under police custody and investigations in the killing launched. Police are suspecting a murder-suicide. Police claim the deceased man was shot dead by an officer under unclear circumstances. The National Treasury has revised the tax bands for salaried workers. Prof Magoha said no child should be denied admission because of unpaid fees for the first term or second term. The national government has not hidden its intent to control the capital city.